Class Production

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cnm.deepdive.abq_film_tour_backend.model.entity.Production
  • @Component
@Entity
public class Production
extends Object
    This entity represents a film or television series with an entry on IMDb. Fields are serialized to be imported directly from the OMDb API.
